snippet.title: Banjo-Kazooie Worlds Collide Trailer (DOWNLOAD IN DESCRIPTION)
snippet.description:
DOWNLOAD LINK: https://drive.google.com/open?id=1j_ZnUjmQ4oFW_JRC4LBPniLQgviCGmeC
Note 3: As of 7/18/2020, the game has been heavily tweaked for improved enjoyment. The hub world has also been remade. Enjoy!
Note 2: As of 9/10/2019, the game has been patched and should now work properly on consoles. Additionally, some minor tweaks have been made to improve the experience. Enjoy!
Note 1: If you downloaded the game before 7:30 PM EST 9/2/2019, redownload it! The original patch had an error that made a certain bonus area inaccessible.

Banjo-Kazooie Worlds Collide is an fanmade, unofficial Banjo Kazooie romhack. Explore 9 worlds and a hub world, each comprised of memories from Banjo-Kazooie games past, complete with a custom soundtrack made of combinations of BK tunes! I hope you enjoy!

(Banjo-Kazooie is owned by Rare.)

This game was made using Banjo's Backpack! Check out the Discord here: https://discord.gg/KSkN3yf4dt
